{"tid":2137751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡志偉：民主派已屬於少數，不應被篩選後才再延任。","createTime":"2020-08-03T07:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:04:01.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"736f1b2500d90bed103ecbf54a7d59e3aee9e594","tid":2137751,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExtYRkc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExtYRkc.jpg&h=695f35d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】被選舉主任裁定提名無效的公民黨黨魁楊岳橋認為，即使由被取消資格的現任議員延任一年，亦不會引起矛盾，民主黨主席胡志偉亦指，若民主派在議會中已屬少數，不應被篩選過才再能延任。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋：「你取消我的資格而已，不是香港人取消我的資格，選舉主任不信任這些人誠意擁護基本法，那過去數年，這些人所做的是甚麼？我不同意我不真誠擁護基本法，這是我清楚的立場，而選舉主任的主觀也是建基於其片面之詞或主觀判斷，這是你的事，我覺得過去數年對得起香港人。」<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉：「如果我們在議會內已是少數，然後我們被挑選過，才能進入(議會)擔任一年，一定要問自己一個問題，究竟所謂何事？如果我們純粹進入議會，批評一下政府，這可能我不在議會也能做到，在外面也能做到，在議會最大的力量是甚麼？我們有重大法案的否決權。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=400317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400317&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=ff13b809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400317&h=3b62e676\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=400317</a><br />\n=====<br />\n<br />\n希望中央能夠寬容D，准許泛民可以延任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁先可以保持否決權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89103211067a0ec48a9fa811965a1209b88d5b22","tid":2137751,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\